<paragraph id="8BD536E4FFA0FF95FF5B49155489F9DE" blockId="44.[151,1436,1518,1940]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">
TYPE LOCALITY. Originally stated as “ 
<collectingCountry id="F37D7674FFA0FF95FD85491454E8F9E3" box="[585,656,1590,1615]" name="Iran" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">Persia</collectingCountry>
or Baluchistan”; restricted by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFFB4B15FFA0FF95FC2349145342F9E3" author="Anderson, S. C. &amp; Leviton, A. E." box="[1007,1338,1590,1615]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" pagination="499 - 534" refId="ref45420" refString="Anderson, S. C. &amp; Leviton, A. E. (1966 b) A review of the genus Ophiomorus with description of three new forms. Proceedings of the California Academy of Sciences, 33, 499 - 534." type="journal article" year="1966">Anderson &amp; Leviton (1966b)</bibRefCitation>
to Chah Bahar [Chabahar], Sistan and Baluchistan Prov., 
<collectingCountry id="F37D7674FFA0FF95FD7149795496F9DE" box="[701,750,1627,1650]" name="Iran" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">Iran</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
